    "stat_block": {
        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "A *flickering* rune causes a weapon to shimmer, grow blurry and indistinct, and momentarily turn invisible at random intervals for a second or two. A *flickering* weapon adds its item bonus from its potency rune to the DC against attempts to Disarm or Steal it. On a critical hit, the weapon flashes bright pulses of color into the creature's eyes, dazzling the creature for 1 round (this effect has the visual trait).",
        "level": 6,
